---
import SectionHeader from "../common/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="category-faq">

  <div class="container">

    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="FAQ"
      title="Frequently Asked Questions"
      description="Answers to common questions about our custom stone sink manufacturing services."
    />

    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>
          What is your minimum order quantity?
        </h3>

        <p>
          We support both sample orders and
          bulk production. MOQ depends on the
          product design and material.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>
          Can you manufacture custom sizes?
        </h3>

        <p>
          Yes. We can customize dimensions,
          basin depth, drain position,
          edge profiles, and surface finishes.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>
          What stone materials are available?
        </h3>

        <p>
          Marble, travertine, limestone,
          granite, quartzite, and many
          other natural stones.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>
          How long is production lead time?
        </h3>

        <p>
          Standard production usually takes
          20–35 days depending on quantity,
          material availability, and project complexity.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h3>
          Do you export worldwide?
        </h3>

        <p>
          Yes. We regularly export to North America,
          Europe, Australia, the Middle East,
          and Southeast Asia.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>